---
import RegionSection from "./RegionSection.astro";
---

<RegionSection

    title="Culture"

    subtitle="The traditions that define life throughout Solmara."

>

<div class="culture-grid">

    <article class="culture-card">

        <h3>🏛️ Architecture</h3>

        <p>

            White stone buildings, open courtyards, colorful marketplaces,
            and lush gardens define the cities and towns of Solmara.

        </p>

    </article>

    <article class="culture-card">

        <h3>👕 Clothing</h3>

        <p>

            Lightweight, breathable clothing is worn throughout the year,
            reflecting Solmara's warm climate and relaxed lifestyle.

        </p>

    </article>

    <article class="culture-card">

        <h3>🍲 Cuisine</h3>

        <p>

            Rich spices, grilled meats, tropical fruits, seafood, and hearty
            dishes inspired by Caribbean, Jamaican, and African flavors.

        </p>

    </article>

    <article class="culture-card">

        <h3>🌸 Bloom Festivals</h3>

        <p>

            Communities gather to celebrate those whose Mana Seeds Bloom,
            filling towns with music, dancing, performances, and feasts.

        </p>

    </article>

    <article class="culture-card">

        <h3>🎵 Music</h3>

        <p>

            Upbeat performances, energetic dancing, and lively street music
            are part of everyday life across Solmara.

        </p>

    </article>

    <article class="culture-card">

        <h3>🎉 Holidays</h3>

        <p>

            Halloween, Day of the Dead, New Year's, and the Day of Eirlys
            are celebrated throughout every kingdom.

        </p>

    </article>

</div>

</RegionSection>

<style>

.culture-grid{

    display:grid;

    grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);

    gap:2rem;

}

.culture-card{

    padding:2.5rem;

    border-radius:22px;

    background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);

    border:1px solid rgba(198,166,107,.15);

    transition:.35s;

}

.culture-card:hover{

    transform:translateY(-8px);

    border-color:var(--primary);

}

.culture-card h3{

    font-family:"Cinzel",serif;

    margin-bottom:1rem;

    font-size:1.8rem;

}

.culture-card p{

    color:var(--muted);

    line-height:1.9;

}

@media(max-width:768px){

.culture-grid{

    grid-template-columns:1fr;

}

}

</style>